            ],
            "text": "recursion"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". DP is deeply rooted in recursive thinking, and without that foundation, the explanations ahead may not fully click. Thankfully, there are already excellent resources on recursionâ€”so spend some time there if needed."
