          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "ðŸŒ How to View Dynamic Programming"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Letâ€™s start by adjusting our perspective. Instead of labeling problems as â€œDP problemsâ€ from the outset, hereâ€™s a better approach:"
