        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Thatâ€™s it. DP is not where we beginâ€”it's the tool we reach for once we've noticed inefficiencies in our recursive logic. And this distinction matters, especially in interviews. Instead of saying, â€œThis is a DP problem,â€ say, â€œThis problem can be improved using DP after we establish a recursive approach.â€"
