      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To systematically break down any DP-style challenge, I follow a 4-step framework. Weâ€™ll explore each step using a well-known example:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
