        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "ðŸ§  Step 2: Add Memoization (Now Youâ€™re Doing DP)"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Once youâ€™ve identified that the recursive solution recalculates the same subproblems repeatedly, it's time to "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
